name: Pine Springs (Devil's Hall)
description:
Introduction

A destination out-and-back hike in Guadalupe Mountains National Park to a short narrowly-carved canyon unique to the area.

The first half of the hike is on trail, the further part of the hike to the narrow geology is in the wash of Pine Spring Canyon.

Time a Fall trip with the turning of the leaves.
